name: Campaign 270: The AI Election / 270号公路：AI大选
description: A bilingual, strategic political simulation game where you race to win the US Presidency. Utilize Gemini AI to navigate complex, humorous, and culturally specific scenarios in battleground states. / 一个双语的策略模拟游戏，利用Gemini AI在摇摆州处理复杂且幽默的政治突发事件，竞选美国总统。
